HEADWORD: Goatee
<hw>Goat`ee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A part of a man's
beard on the chin or lower lip which is allowed to grow, and trimmed so
as to resemble the beard of a goat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

